Hi Carlo,

Thanks for your tutorial.  How (assuming that you are using Windows) will you solve this code, without getting the maximum number of threads error? (OS limit in windows)

  

N <- 130

fvec <- vector(length=N, mode="list")

for (i in 1:N) {

 fname <- paste0("C:/temp/foo", i, ".tmp")

 fvec[[i]] <- file(fname, "w")

}

Sys.sleep(3)

for (i in 1:N) {

 close(fvec[[i]])

}
